<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>Fleet Tools</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/index.css">
        <script src = "https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.4.min.js"></script>
        <script src = "../static/index.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class = "left-column">
            <h1>Fleet Tools</h1>
            <p>by American Pacific</p>
            <h3>Selected Game:</h3>
            {% if game %}
                <p id="game-label">{{ game }}</p>
            {% else %}
                <p id="game-label">None</p>
            {% endif %}            
        </div>
        <div class = "main">
            <h1>Hello! ðŸ‘‹</h1>
            <p>Welcome to fleet tools for Airline Club and MyFly Club by American Pacific.</p>
            <p>If you've never played the games, you should check out <a href="https://www.airline-club.com">Airline Club</a> and <a href="https://myfly.club">MyFly.Club</a></p>
            <h2>Using Fleet Tools:</h2>
            <p>Some of the fleet tools require specificying two dates to compare, but not all. All of them require you select a game though, so you should do that.</p>
            <div class="game-select">
                <h3>Select the game you want to use:</h3>
                <button type="button", id="ac">
                    AC
                </button>
                <button type="button", id="mfc">
                    MFC
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="date-select">
                <div class="select-start-date">
                    {% if game %}
                        <h3>Select earlier date for comparision:</h3>
                        {% for date in dates %}
                            <button type="button" id="{{ date[0] }}{{ date[1 ]}}{{ date[2] }}start">
                                {{ date[0] }} {{ date[1] }}, {{ date[2]}}
                            </button>
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif%}
                </div>
                <div class="select-end-date">
                    {% if game %}
                        <h3>Select later date for comparision:</h3>
                        {% for date in dates %}
                             <button type="button" id="{{ date[0] }}{{ date[1 ]}}{{ date[2] }}end">
                                {{ date[0] }} {{ date[1] }}, {{ date[2]}}
                            </button>
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif%}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>